Package: jsonr
Type: Package
Title: Advanced JSON Manipulation Tools for R
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2025-04-13
Authors@R: 
    person("Christian", "Luechtenborg", email = "christian.luechtenborg@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Advanced tools for manipulating JSON data in R. The package provides 
    functions for adding elements to specific paths in JSON objects, inserting 
    properties into nested array elements, and other JSON manipulation tasks. 
    It offers a more flexible and powerful approach to working with complex 
    JSON structures than what is available in base packages.
